    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for MRL 2 Class II device context. Hemolysis index predictions fall within the 20% acceptance threshold across all validation operating points. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Assessment package accepted for inclusion in 510(k) regulatory submission.",
